You instantly know the answer to any mathematical equation that you speak aloud. The equation must be a problem that an intelligent creature with a mathematics education could solve using nonmagical tools within 1 hour of calculation. Additionally, you gain +1 [[impact]] on the next attempt you make within the next hour that involves engineering or inventing something.